\c 26
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli babalwa elizweni lakoMowabi
\p
\v 1 Kwathi emva kwenhlupheko iN\nd kosi\nd* yakhuluma kuMozisi lakuEleyazare indodana kaAroni umpristi, isithi:
\v 2 Thathani inani lonke lenhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 30.12. Nani 1.2. Eks. 38.25,26.\x*, kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amabili langaphezulu, ngezindlu zaboyise, bonke aba\add nga\add*phuma ukuya empini koIsrayeli\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 3 UMozisi loEleyazare umpristi basebekhuluma labo emagcekeni akoMowabi\x + 26.63. 22.1.\x*, eJordani eJeriko, besithi:
\v 4 \add Babale\add* kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amabili langaphezulu\x + 26.2.\x*, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi labantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 1.1.\x* abaphuma elizweni leGibhithe.
\p
\v 5 URubeni, izibulo likaIsrayeli. Amadodana kaRubeni: UHanoki, \add okwavela kuye\add* usendo lwabakoHanoki; koPalu, usendo lwabakoPalu;
\v 6 koHezironi, usendo lwabakoHezironi; koKarimi, usendo lwabakoKarimi\x + Gen. 46.8,9. Eks. 6.14. 1 Lan. 5.1-4.\x*.
\v 7 Lezi zinsendo zabakoRubeni; lalabo ababalwayo babo babeyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane lantathu lamakhulu ayisikhombisa lamatshumi amathathu\x + 1.21.\x*.
\v 8 Lamadodana kaPalu; uEliyabi.
\v 9 Lamadodana kaEliyabi; oNemuweli loDathani loAbiramu. Yibo oDathani loAbiramu, ababizwa yinhlangano\x + 1.16; 16.2.\x*, abaphikisana loMozisi loAroni\x + Hlab. 60.1.\x*, eqenjini likaKora, lapho bephikisana leN\nd kosi\x + Hlab. 60.1.\x*\nd*.
\v 10 Lomhlaba wavula umlomo wawo, wabaginya loKora ekufeni kwaleloqembu\x + 16.32,35.\x*, lapho umlilo waqothula amadoda angamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amahlanu; asesiba yisibonelo\x + 16.38. 1 Kor. 10.6. 2 Pet. 2.6.\x*.
\v 11 Kodwa abantwana bakaKora kabafanga\x + Eks. 6.24. 1 Lan.6.22.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Amadodana kaSimeyoni ngensendo zawo\x + Gen. 46.10. Eks. 6.15. 1 Lan. 4.24.\x*: KoNemuweli, usendo lwabakoNemuweli; koJamini, usendo lwabakoJamini; koJakini, usendo lwabakoJakini;
\v 13 koZera, usendo lwabakoZera; koShawuli, usendo lwabakoShawuli.
\v 14 Lezi zinsendo zabakoSimeyoni; izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lambili lamakhulu amabili\x + 1.23; 25.9,14.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Amadodana kaGadi ngensendo zawo\x + Gen. 46.16.\x*: KoZefoni, usendo lwabakoZefoni; koHagi, usendo lwabakoHagi; koShuni, usendo lwabakoShuni;
\v 16 koOzini, usendo lwabakoOzini; koEri, usendo lwabakoEri;
\v 17 koArodi, usendo lwabakoArodi; koAreli, usendo lwabakoAreli.
\v 18 Lezi zinsendo zamadodana kaGadi, njengababaliweyo babo, inkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 1.25.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Amadodana kaJuda\x + Gen. 38.3-10.46.12. 1 Lan. 2.3-5.\x* ayengoEri loOnani; oEri loOnani basebefela elizweni leKhanani.
\v 20 Njalo amadodana kaJuda ngensendo zawo yila: KoShela, usendo lwabakoShela; koPerezi, usendo lwabakoPerezi; koZera, usendo lwabakoZera.
\v 21 Lamadodana kaPerezi yila: KoHezironi, usendo lwabakoHezironi; koHamuli, usendo lwabakoHamuli.
\v 22 Lezi zinsendo zikaJuda, njengababaliweyo babo, inkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisikhombisa lesithupha lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 1.27.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Amadodana kaIsakari ngensendo zawo\x + Gen. 46.13. 1 Lan. 7.1.\x*: \add K\add*oThola, usendo lwabakoThola; koPhuwa, usendo lwabakoPhuwa;
\v 24 koJashubi, usendo lwabakoJashubi; koShimroni, usendo lwabakoShimroni.
\v 25 Lezi zinsendo zikaIsakari, njengababaliweyo babo, inkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisithupha lane lamakhulu amathathu\x + 1.29.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Amadodana kaZebuluni ngensendo zawo\x + Gen. 46.14.\x*: KoSeredi, usendo lwabakoSeredi; koEloni, usendo lwabakoEloni; koJaleli, usendo lwabakoJaleli.
\v 27 Lezi zinsendo zabakoZebuloni, njengababaliweyo babo, inkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisithupha lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 1.31.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Amadodana kaJosefa\x + Gen. 46.20.Nani 26.37. 1 Lan. 7.14-20.\x* ngensendo zawo ayengoManase loEfrayimi.
\v 29 Amadodana kaManase: KoMakiri, usendo lwabakoMakiri\x + Josh. 17.1,2.\x*; uMakiri wasezala uGileyadi; koGileyadi, usendo lwabakoGileyadi.
\v 30 La ngamadodana kaGileyadi: \add K\add*oIyezeri, usendo lwabakoIyezeri; koHeleki, usendo lwabakoHeleki;
\v 31 la\add ko\add*Asiriyeli, usendo lwabakoAsiriyeli; la\add ko\add*Shekema, usendo lwabakoShekema;
\v 32 la\add ko\add*Shemida, usendo lwabakoShemida; la\add ko\add*Heferi, usendo lwabakoHeferi.
\p
\v 33 Njalo uZelofehadi indodana kaHeferi\x + 27.1. 36.11. Josh. 17.3.\x* wayengelamadodana, kodwa amadodakazi. Lamabizo amadodakazi kaZelofehadi ayengoMahla, loNowa, uHogila, uMilka, loTiriza.
\v 34 Lezi zinsendo zikaManase, lababaliweyo babo, inkulungwane ezingamatshumi amahlanu lambili lamakhulu ayisikhombisa\x + 1.35.\x*.
\p
\v 35 La ngamadodana kaEfrayimi ngensendo zawo: KoShuthela, usendo lwabakoShuthela; koBekeri, usendo lwabakoBekeri; koTahani, usendo lwabakoTahani.
\v 36 Lala ngamadodana kaShuthela: KoErani, usendo lwabakoErani.
\v 37 Lezi zinsendo zamadodana kaEfrayimi, njengababaliweyo babo, inkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu lambili lamakhulu amahlanu\x + 1.33.\x*. La ngamadodana kaJosefa ngensendo zawo.
\p
\v 38 Amadodana kaBhenjamini ngensendo zawo\x + Gen. 46.21. 1 Lan. 7.6. 8.1-4.\x*: KoBhela, usendo lwabakoBhela; koAshibeli, usendo lwabakoAshibeli; koAhiramu, usendo lwabakoAhiramu;
\v 39 koShefufamu, usendo lwabakoShefufamu; koHufamu, usendo lwabakoHufamu.
\v 40 Lamadodana kaBhela ayenguAridi loNamani: \add KoAridi\add*, usendo lwabakoAridi; koNamani, usendo lwabakoNamani.
\v 41 La ngamadodana kaBhenjamini ngensendo zawo; lababaliweyo babo babeyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane lanhlanu lamakhulu ayisithupha\x + 1.37.\x*.
\p
\v 42 La ngamadodana kaDani ngensendo zawo\x + Gen.46.23.\x*: KoShuhamu, usendo lwabakoShuhamu. Lezi zinsendo zikaDani ngensendo zazo.
\v 43 Zonke insendo zabakoShuhamu, njengababaliweyo babo, babeyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisithupha lane lamakhulu amane.
\p
\v 44 Amadodana kaAsheri ngensendo zawo\x + Gen. 46.17. 1 Lan. 7.30,31.\x*: KoJimna, usendo lwabakoJimna; koIshivi, usendo lwabakoIshivi; koBeriya, usendo lwabakoBeriya.
\v 45 Kumadodana kaBeriya: KoHeberi, usendo lwabakoHeberi; koMalikiyeli, usendo lwabakoMalikiyeli.
\v 46 Lebizo lendodakazi kaAsheri lalinguSera.
\v 47 Lezi zinsendo zamadodana kaAsheri, njengababaliweyo babo; inkulungwane ezingamatshumi amahlanu lantathu lamakhulu amane\x + 1.41.\x*.
\p
\v 48 Amadodana kaNafithali ngensendo zawo\x + Gen. 46.24. 1 Lan. 7.13.\x*: KoJazeli, usendo lwabakoJazeli; koGuni, usendo lwabakoGuni;
\v 49 koJezeri, usendo lwabakoJezeri; koShilema, usendo lwabakoShilema.
\v 50 Lezi zinsendo zikaNafithali ngensendo zazo; lababaliweyo babo babeyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane lanhlanu lamakhulu amane\x + 1.43.\x*.
\p
\v 51 Laba ngababaliweyo babantwana bakoIsrayeli, inkulungwane ezingamakhulu ayisithupha lanye lamakhulu ayisikhombisa lamatshumi amathathu\x + 1.46.\x*.
\s Ilizwe lehlukaniswa ngenkatho
\p
\v 52 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 53 Kulaba ilizwe lizakwehlukaniswa libe yilifa njengenani lamabizo\x + Josh. 11.23; 14.1.\x*.
\v 54 Kwabanengi uzakwengeza ilifa labo, lakwabalutshwana uzanciphisa ilifa labo; ngulowo lalowo uzanikwa ilifa lakhe njengababaliweyo bakhe.
\v 55 Loba kunjalo ilizwe lizakwehlukaniswa ngenkatho; ngokwamabizo ezizwe zaboyise bazalidla ilifa\x + 33.54. 34.13. Josh. 11.23. 14.2.\x*.
\v 56 Ngokwenkatho ilifa lalo lizakwehlukaniswa phakathi kwabanengi labalutshwana.
\s Isizwe sakoLevi
\p
\v 57 Lalaba ngababalwayo bamaLevi ngensendo zawo\x + Gen. 46.11. Eks. 6.16-19. 1 Lan. 6.1; 6.16-22.\x*; koGerishoni, usendo lwabakoGerishoni; koKohathi, usendo lwabakoKohathi; koMerari, usendo lwabakoMerari.
\v 58 Laba zinsendo zabakoLevi; usendo lwabakoLibini, usendo lwabakoHebroni, usendo lwabakoMahli, usendo lwabakoMushi, usendo lwabakoKora. UKohathi wasezala uAmramu.
\v 59 Lebizo lomkaAmramu lalinguJokebedi, indodakazi kaLevi\x + Eks. 2.1,2,4. 6.20.\x*, \add unina\add* owamzalela uLevi eGibhithe; njalo wamzalela uAmramu oAroni loMozisi loMiriyamu udadewabo.
\v 60 UAroni wazalelwa uNadabi loAbihu, uEleyazare loIthamari\x + 3.2. 1 Lan. 24.1.\x*.
\v 61 Kodwa uNadabi loAbihu bafa lapho banikela umlilo ongejwayelekanga phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Levi 10.1.\x*\nd*.
\v 62 Lababalwayo babo babeyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lantathu, bonke abesilisa kusukela kolenyanga kusiya phezulu\x + 3.39.\x*; ngoba babengabalelwanga phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 1.49.\x*, ngoba babenganikwanga ilifa phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 18.20.\x*.
\p
\v 63 Laba ngababalwa nguMozisi loEleyazare umpristi, ababala abantwana bakoIsrayeli emagcekeni akoMowabi eJordani eJeriko\x + 26.3. 22.1.\x*.
\v 64 Kodwa phakathi kwalabo kwakungekho muntu wababalwayo nguMozisi loAroni umpristi, lapho bebala abantwana bakoIsrayeli enkangala yeSinayi\x + 1.44. Dute. 2.14,15.\x*;
\v 65 ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayithe ngabo: Bazakufa lokufa enkangala\x + 14.28,29. 1 Kor. 10.5.\x*. Njalo kakusalanga muntu kubo ngaphandle kukaKalebi indodana kaJefune, loJoshuwa indodana kaNuni\x + 13.6.\x*.
